+ New menu item 'array element'.
+ New hotkeys \sa, \sas.
+ New submenu 'Snippets'.
+ Hotkeys for the POSIX character classes.
+ Hardcopy (run menu) can print any buffer.
+ Bugfix: 'Run->save + run script' (\rr, <C-F9>) : visual mode broken. 
+ Minor improvements.

